## Logging Format
All tests log with consistent format:
```
[VISUAL] {Component} {variant} - {status}
```

Statuses:
- `captured` - Screenshot taken successfully
- `passed` - No visual diff detected
- `failed` - Visual diff detected
- `skipped` - Test skipped (condition not met)

## Failure Output
On failure, Playwright generates:
1. Expected screenshot
2. Actual screenshot
3. Diff screenshot highlighting changes

Test output:
```
[VISUAL] PromptCard light mode default - FAILED
  Expected: baseline/prompt-card-light-default.png
  Actual: test-results/prompt-card-light-default-actual.png
  Diff: test-results/prompt-card-light-default-diff.png

  Difference: 2,547 pixels (5.2%)
  Max allowed: 100 pixels
```

